      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing... it doesn't feel like i'm \"doing my best.\" it just feels like i'm a ghost. like the real me is already gone and i'm just performing the duties of a person. there's no spark left, no substance. i'm just existing out of habit, and honestly, it feels more like a burden than a life at this point.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
