    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you're supposed to say that, but it doesn't feel temporary. it feels like a finished chapter. if the person i was is truly gone, then what is the point of maintaining this shell? it feels so much more logical to just let go than to keep pretending there's something left to save.",
